<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-8 offset-2">
      <div class="card mt-4">
        <div id="stats" class="card-body">
          <h5 id="userStats" class="card-title">User Stats</h5>
          <p>
            <strong>ID</strong>: {{example.id}}</p>
          <p>
            <p>
              <strong>Name</strong>: {{example.name}}</p>
            <p>
              <p>
                <strong>Age:</strong> {{example.age}}</p>
              <p>
                <strong>Height</strong>: {{example.height}} inches
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Weight</strong>: {{example.weight}} lbs
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Goal</strong>: {{example.goal}}
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Physical Activity</strong>: {{example.activity}}
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Sex</strong>: {{example.sex}}
              </p>

              <a id="breadcrumb" href="/">‚Üê Back To Home</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-8 offset-2">
      <!-- USER RESULTS IN COLLAPSIBLE BOXES -->
      <ul class="collapsible">
        <li>
          <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>BMR</div>
          <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Based off of your physical stats, your Basal Metabolic Rate (BMR) is: <br> {{bmr}} </span></div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>BMR + Activity Level</div>
          <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Based off of your BMR plus your Activity Factor, your BMR is: <br> {{bmrAct}}</span></div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>BMR Based on Goals</div>
          <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Our daily recommended caloric intake based on your statistics and goal is: <br> {{bmrRec}}</span></div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="collapsible-header"><i class="material-icons">expand_more</i>Macronutrients</div>
          <div class="collapsible-body"><span>Your macronutrient breakdown is: <br> {{proteins}} grams of protein <br> {{fats}} grams of fat <br> {{carbz}} grams of carbohydrates </span></div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>





